query: SELECT a.id, a.accountName, a.accountPlan, a.accountStatus, a.accountOwnerUserId, s.subStatus, p.planKey FROM accounts a LEFT JOIN subscriptions s ON s.subAccountId = a.id LEFT JOIN plans p ON p.id = s.subPlanId ORDER BY a.id
